txt.en: Shíktarb is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nBring the Orkish blades to Shíktarb.

'Listen up! Some coward Orcs dropped their weapons on the battlefield! You better go get them before those Men do!\n\n'Bring them back here and I'll personally hand them over to some Orcs who deserve a weapon!'
Bring the Orkish blades to Shíktarb
Shíktarb commands you to search the battlefield of Osgiliath for dropped Orkish blades so that more Orcs may be armed with deadly weapons.
'You brought back quite a few! That means there were more worthless Orcs than I thought. You better not let me down if you want to stay in my favour!'
Orkish blades can be found on the Eastern side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should collect Orkish blades.
